<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="write-v">write <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /raɪt/    美 /raɪt/  </p>
<p>(wrote, written)</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>写；书写；写信：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The pen writes smoothly. 
这支笔书写流畅。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>write a letter to sb 
给某人写信</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t forget to <strong>write to</strong> me. 
记得写信给我。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="write-back">write back</h3>
<p>1.<strong>回信：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I received his letter two weeks ago, but I forgot to write back.
我两星期前收到了他的信，但忘了给他回信。</p></div>

<h3 id="write-down">write down</h3>
<p>1.<strong>写下；记下：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wrote down new words and added them to my collection. 
我记下新单词，加入到我自己的词汇表里。</p></div>

<h3 id="write-up">write up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>(根据笔记) 写成文</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The article was w <strong><em>_</em></strong>_in German and translated into Chinese.  （2005 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. written  </p></div>